                <note rend="inline" type="source">103.9169 Bogotá: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Colombia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Daniels</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-05-16">May 16,
                            1944</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>649. From FEA, for La Spina. Embassy’s A–849, May 5. Suggest you do not postpone
                    processing of import recommendations. When possible you will be informed on
                    categories to be eliminated from decentralization, July 1, 1944. [FEA.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
